        The primary government and industry source documents behind the policy backdrop
        OPDA works inside — the UK Industrial Strategy, the Smart Data scheme, and the
        property-market reform programme. Local copies are archived under <code>source/</code>
        where available; otherwise the canonical gov.uk URL is given.
      </p>

