        <li><a href="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/69c11f9ed588c92c483e4b66/smart-data-strategy.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>DBT Smart Data Strategy</strong></a> — the government's strategy for Smart Data across the economy (gov.uk).</li>
        <li><a class="resource-link" href="/resource?path=source/08-external-references/uk-government/understanding-the-costs-and-benefits-of-smart-data-use-cases-research-report.pdf"><code>Economic Impact Analysis — costs and benefits of Smart Data use cases</code></a> — DBT-commissioned research report.</li>
